of completely.  You should be able to bash, kick, spit, flip off....and yes...even backstab while on a horse....if I have a back......you gave me a spear for a reason right?<br><br>You could scale this...depending on what type of horse is purchased.  I paid 109k in plat, considering the limitations.....there are probably one or two zones that I could actually hastle free use this horse.<br><br>I am not a caster, obviously, and the benefits are not the same. (Being able to med and cast and never have to stand)<br> <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4347"><IMG src="http://www.nwlink.com/~bstevens/Rogues/images/viscer1.jpg" border=0></a><br><a href=http://www.casus-belli.net><I>Casus Belli</I></a>-An Occasion for War<BR>Ayonae Ro<BR>"You can run but you'll just die tired"--KAAOS</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufendrick.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fendrick</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/31/02 3:28:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23113.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: You can lead a horse to water.......</span><hr size=1> yeah horses have to be tweaked to make them worth it. but i for one am glad they are so damn expensive. when i heard about the introduction of horses in SoL, i was like, crap now everyone is always gonna be riding these goofy looking horses. im glad it did not turn out like that <p>-Fen</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umakabrei.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Makabrei</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/31/02 4:38:16 pm)</font><br>   <a hre